#  Variable           Optional  Values          Explanation
#  ----------------------------------------------------------------------
#  V			opt.	0 or 1		Sets the verbosity level
#						(only from command line)
#  BUILD_VERBOSE	opt.	0 or 1		Same as above.
#						Can be set anywhere.
#  EXTRA_CFLAGS
#  EXTRA_CPPFLAGS
#  EXTRA_LDFLAGS
